Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:09.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:12.70,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! So juicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:19.56,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No sign of the goblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.14,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they aren't coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.96,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lower our guard, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:29.23,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Crusty's forward strike force has \Nreached Narashino, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:33.38,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,They're heading toward the main goblin battalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:37.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Their fight might decide our fate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:40.31,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Serara...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:43.28,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.24,HUD1,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Kasumi Lake, West{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NZantleaf Peninsula/ Kasumi Lake \N Field/ Monsters Present \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NEvents/ The Goblin King's Return
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.91,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Direct strike to the enemy vanguard's center.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.68,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, the main attack force can now advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.90,Monsters,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hill Giant, Lv. 72          Hill Giant, Lv. 80 \NRank/ Raid 1          Rank/ Raid 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements. Two hill giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Healers should flank both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Start by annihilating the smaller side groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Main force, continue to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:50.95,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:06.36,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,enjoying the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:10.85,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:16.07,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he seem so sad? So lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:22.74,Title,L,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1569,1)}Chasing After Them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.10,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing After Them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.74,HUD1,L,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Midraunt Equestrian Park{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NLeague of Freedom Cities, Eastal/ Funabashi Area \N No Monsters \NNo PVP \NSkill Use Permitted \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NEvents/ The Goblin King's Return
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.28,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.10,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Resupply team 5, depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:30.55,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Continue to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:32.26,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.77,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintain position until further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.22,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,This is Narashino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.79,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,As planned, we've rendezvoused.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Understood. Location confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.11,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,The Ocypete has met up with \Nthe second Akihabara group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please confirm location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:45.30,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Once they complete some maintenance, \Nthey'll set out for Choushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:49.81,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the telepathy communication \Nnetwork is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:54.62,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Each squad has a leader, and squads \Ncan communicate with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:59.82,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,And they have a contact at headquarters \Nwith whom they can speak, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:04.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This supports smooth communication among squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.82,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Crusty and his force are kicking butt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.78,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's going well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.16,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Choushi is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.06,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Victory isn't going to be overly hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But after the battle ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the goblins will flee in all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:24.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They might attack the People of the Land's villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:29.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent this, we've been surrounding \Nthe goblins as we attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leading them to a single point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But we must also protect the town of Choushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Or our encirclement will be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Choushi is the most \Ncritical point in this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.49,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But until all platoons have \Ndeployed, I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.40,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.44,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.80,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,"With what"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:22.69,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I, Rundel Haus Code, \Nam in perfect shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.56,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like no one in the world can stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good, all clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.33,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it will stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:39.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If we all work together, the goblins are nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.81,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:57.09,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than a few hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.60,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand, I'd imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If that many rush into the town together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:07.79,Default - italics,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let the kids do anything reckless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.42,Default - italics,M,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Marielle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit them first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.91,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's destroy them before \Nthey can reach the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.41,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta, let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.17,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.17,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.43,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the order to fire everyone up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:38.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you for all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Help us out just a bit more... \NJust one more fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:45.20,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:46.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:48.32,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.82,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's split into teams, \Nto be ready for a second wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:58.45,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya, our party will focus on support.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.62,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:07.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The camp group, in Choushi, has just \Nmade contact with the sahuagin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:12.23,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There are sixty adventurers and \Nat least a thousand sahuagin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They're overwhelmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the Ocypete to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.23,SignB,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}135 km Remaining to Meinion Coast \N{\fs16}(Half Gaia distance)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.43,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:45.91,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, our job is to recover our MP.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.33,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.35,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Whirlwind Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.76,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya has grown stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:07.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He still has a ways to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But he'll get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.64,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.99,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,She used to only think about healing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:19.41,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Wolfy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:30.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But now she's using offensive techniques, \Nand remembering to summon her companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:35.47,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the bard girl and the sorcerer boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.18,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Dance of Pavane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:45.56,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,They back each other up as if they can \Nunderstand each other's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.85,Default - italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Burned Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.65,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Rundel Haus is a walking bundle of vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:57.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's putting all his feeling and \Nemotion into his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.12,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy, try to keep your output down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.24,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:02.95,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Serara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.68,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,We're good on healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.62,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Go back on attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.97,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.34,HUD Big,Se,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Guardian Barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.34,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Eight seconds until Guardian Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.34,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Minori keeps a constant eye on \Nthe big picture as she fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Her friends' teamwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:18.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,enemy location,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:20.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,enemy encounter order,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,enemy defeat order...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.83,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Like writing each enemy defeat as a sentence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,each battle as a chapter,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and collecting all those chapters \Ninto a book called {\i1}Tactics{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.52,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,The way she's fighting is just like Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:41.41,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,To the percent, and in thirty-second increments,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.83,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I think he meant that he was fighting by \Nlooking thirty seconds into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,One percent is how closely he \Ntracks his allies' remaining MP.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.30,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tracking the MP of allies in different classes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is impossible without monitoring the status screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:03.37,Default,Rank,0000,0000,0000,,But he can track it to a percent,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.87,Monsters,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Luceheart of the Seven Prisons, Lv. 95        Mad Carousel Golem, Lv. 82\N\NBonus Damage: 1000P                                                              Rank/ Raid 1 \N\NMove Speed Decreased                                                      Lapis Fly, Lv. 84 \NAccuracy Decreased                                                          Dodge Decreased \NRank/ Raid 1                                                                              Rank/ Party
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.39,Default,Rank,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the enemy status,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:06.16,HUD1,Rank,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta\NStatus/ In Combat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.45,HUD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.85,Default,Rank,0000,0000,0000,,to predict where the battle \Nwill be in thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:13.39,Default,Rank,0000,0000,0000,,He makes everything proceed \Nthe way he wants it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Shiro's fully controlled combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The full-control encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.42,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya, move back a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.74,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Serara, group heal, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.24,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.50,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we actually live in this world now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I doubt he can see a full thirty \Nseconds ahead, as he once could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:40.00,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But what Minori's attempting is, \Nwithout doubt, an imitation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Shiro's full-control encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:47.23,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Minori is chasing after Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:51.25,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows how many seconds \Nahead she can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.25,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:02.14,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It's the druid's special attack \Nmagic, Shrieker Echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.55,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I had Serara set it up as a warning system!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.93,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the goblins are returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.01,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.50,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.54,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, you do your best, too, Nyanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.22,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.22,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:23.94,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,We can handle the goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:28.10,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Isuzu the bard is with us, \Nso we have good sustain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.03,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.64,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Minori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.39,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the operator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:45.24,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Serara, focus on healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.41,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the field monitor, Minori...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:52.05,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle keeping up everyone's MP.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:53.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Goblins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.70,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.38,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get them all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.44,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,But the samurai skills aren't fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:07.34,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.12,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:12.60,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I shall show you the beautiful \Nmelody of my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.90,Default - italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Serpent Bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.09,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.87,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Slow Snail's Ballad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.75,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Head Splitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.75,Default - italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Frost Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:42.77,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Dis—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.59,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.50,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.16,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I got mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.20,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.27,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Isuzu, did you see
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:58.06,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,my lovely magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.95,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I sure did. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:07.03,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It sort of feels like you're making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.26,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.67,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.38,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.67,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not making fun of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.37,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.63,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I can only see five seconds ahead, \Nin five-percent increments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.22,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm lucky, maybe ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.54,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it as well as Shiroe yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:25.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That close to the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:26.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:36.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Ocypete will be there in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.86,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, reinforcements will arrive in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.11,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.47,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:56.76,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.10,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.98,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy's MP is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.55,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,How long will this fight take?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.30,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Marielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:10.68,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,A ship carrying reinforcements will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:14.25,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes, they'll be able \Nto send some help our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.33,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more... Let's keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.96,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Good... I was getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.52,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.79,Monsters,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Dire Wolf, Lv. 32 \NRank/ Party
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A dire wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.79,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,And it isn't alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.15,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Willow Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:23.17,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Spell: Prayer to the Four Quarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.88,HUD1,Se,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Minori
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.99,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.32,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Serara, focus on the dire wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.85,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,But then I can't heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.16,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the healing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:45.32,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Two dire wolves and the hobgoblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.64,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,If they attack at once, Tohya won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.85,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:53.36,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,you take the hobgoblins \Nand one of the wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.52,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy! Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.80,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Prayer to the Four Quarters will \Nlast another thirty-two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:16:59.94,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Before it runs out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.17,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.00,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:10.38,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,When you encounter a difficult opponent, \Nthere are a number of different strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.94,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,One example is to eliminate the weaker ones first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:17.33,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,By lowering the number of potential attackers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.98,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,you also limit the amount of damage they deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.10,Default - italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Frigid Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.98,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Resonance Beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:40.74,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:51.74,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Isuzu, we must eliminate \Nthat other dire wolf now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:52.42,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:00.99,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:06.06,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,The healing can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.65,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Two dire wolves and the hobgoblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.85,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,If Tohya's HP keeps going down like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:16.20,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,In nine seconds, Tohya will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:20.96,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Eight seconds until I can cast \NPurification Barrier again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:26.46,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,No, a barrier like that won't \Nwork against these opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.59,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,If Tohya loses...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.07,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,If he loses...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:48.79,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:49.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:52.23,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.35,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the doggies to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:56.38,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.32,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy, you're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:59.46,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Miss Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:02.99,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to these mutts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.70,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.95,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I am Rundel Haus Code...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:26.18,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,An adventurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.55,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.30,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.34,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.12,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nature Revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.67,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,The revival spell isn't working?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.39,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Minori, try another!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.78,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Soul-call Prayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.34,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.53,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:26.57,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy... Rudy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.01,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of the People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:42.61,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,He joined our party, \Nadventured with us, ate with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.00,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,But Rudy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.18,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,Adding you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.68,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.07,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.00,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of the People of the Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.59,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Would you keep it secret from \Nthe others, Miss Isuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.01,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:15.75,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:23.63,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.72,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Why he was so desperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:40.11,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell him that he \Ncouldn't be an adventurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.03,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Rudy is one of \Nthe People of the Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can't revive him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:53.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Serara, try another revival spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:56.17,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,It's still on cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:59.63,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a healing spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:15.48,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,When I heal him, it feels like \Nthere's some small response...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:21.48,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:23.45,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,If reviving doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:26.10,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,There's still hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:30.78,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Help us, please... Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:35.48,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, we need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:08.42,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Rundel Haus is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:09.69,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,He is one of the People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:11.80,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The People of the Land cannot revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:13.78,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,That is the law of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.78,0:24:15.35,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,But to grant Minori's wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:17.53,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe challenges the laws...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.41,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,For a true friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who would travel the world with you to \Nfind a dawn that no one has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:30.99,Title,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Contract
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.49,0:24:25.33,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.33,0:24:27.69,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,We will change the world.
